Package org.universAAL.utilities.api.service

Contains raw helper classes to deal with Service concepts of universAAL.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Add
    Class representing an Add-type argument in a service request.
    Arg
    Helper class to build arguments in a service request.
    Change
    Class representing a Change-type argument in a service request.
    Output
    Class representing an Output-type argument in a service request.
    Path
    Helper class to build property paths in a service request.
    Remove
    Class representing a Remove-type argument in a service request.
    Typematch
    Class representing a Type-match argument in a service request.
    Value
    Abstract class representing an argument in a service request.
    Variable
    Class representing a Variable-Input-type argument in a service request.
